reviewText:
This game is years old, taken from Amazon (Release Date: 22 July 2011) Of course not a suprise to see it on Steam since anything can get on here. Bought it in the Groupees $0.50 bundle. Don't buy it.

2/10 For having a barely working physics engine with atleast a competent amount of blast control.

reviewText: Bought this game expecting a fun sandbox game, but I got a game with poor graphics, awkward contols (sensitivity is very high, unable to change), and just boring gameplay. This game is NOT worth your money. Hell, I wouldn't install it if it were free. Most MOBILE games are better than this. The game looks like it was created in 30 minutes. And whoever programmed the controls was probably drunk. Refunded and uninstalled,
